  <h2>About</h2>
  <p><a href="http://sweetandsour.fm/">Sweet and Sour</a> is a podcast dedicated to capturing the common threads and the nuance of the Asian American experience. In our episodes, we'll discuss topics such as activism, education, relationships, food, family, media representation, language, Asian Americans' relation to other minorities, etc. Expect 25-50 minute episodes every two weeks.</p>
